{"tid":523011,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD Zen+ 12nm Ryzen和X470主機板將在四月份推出，第二代Ryzen Threadripper下半年推出","createTime":"2018-01-08T06:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T06:24:57.000Z","uid":58882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ed4bd77cf88d501ca33f88d2e65c17abd86a3a","tid":523011,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"AMD已經在官方的新聞資料中確認，第二代Ryzen高性能CPU將於2018年4月推出，AMD承諾首款12nm Zen+處理器將擁有更高的實脈並支援Precision Boost 2技術。<br />\n此外AMD已經確認，Ryzen CPU的第二代晶片組X470也將於2018年4月推出。據AMD稱X470平台將針對第二代Ryzen CPU進行優化。<br />\nAMD第二代Ryzen Threadripper將於2018年下半年推出<br />\n另外官方路線圖證實，Ryzen 2nd Gen將於2018年第二季推出，而另外第二代Ryzen Threadripper系列將會在2018年下半年發佈更新，同時還將推出第二代Ryzen PRO系列。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/140955_31a603af449b36f9f5fca12752eacaec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F140955_31a603af449b36f9f5fca12752eacaec.jpg&h=c1ed06bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/140956_8e54f1b35c4c0ddea2c2fd840381103d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F140956_8e54f1b35c4c0ddea2c2fd840381103d.jpg&h=d2a71761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/140956_b57874546c6adee6b3f586a3f5029a27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F140956_b57874546c6adee6b3f586a3f5029a27.jpg&h=0492ed38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink : <a href=\"http://www.xfastest.com/thread-204208-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fthread-204208-1-1.html&d=MIfc805xsXb52afwCfAEhMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c44230a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xfastest.com/thread-204208-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"60c3fedf95cc2341afd737bcc4149340314248bb","tid":5230